  "informal_statement": "For every positive real x, x + 1/x ≥ 2.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "x + 1/x - 2 = (x-1)²/x, which is nonnegative since x > 0. Clear the denominator with field_simp, rewrite, and close with positivity.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem add_one_div_ge_two (x : ℝ) (hx : 0 < x) : 2 ≤ x + 1 / x",
